drafts_about: Below are your cloud drafts. We store them so that you can easily continue writing messages when switching between devices. For example, you can start typing a message on your phone on the way to work and finish it on your keyboard when you get there. To delete a draft, simply delete the text in the input field in the respective Telegram chat.
